{"tid":184074,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［長文慎入］屌我妹條臭閪真係好撚on9","createTime":"2017-04-02T14:27:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-02T15:34:31.000Z","uid":29719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9ec562f3609d3f04da86ca7e4b0d9eaac62015cf","tid":184074,"uid":29719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:27:26.000Z","msg":"佢聽日家政堂，整蛋糕，之後佢話係屋企試整一次先<br />\n<br />\n咁好啦，佢落完街一轉之後就開始整喇<br />\n<br />\n點知佢乜撚柒都買唔齊，又冇買到牛奶，又冇牛油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但佢又懶得再落街買，於是佢就開始亂鳩咁黎<br />\n<br />\n冇牛奶，就用我爺啲老人家奶粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n冇牛油，就用之前食m記早餐用剩個三四嚿牛油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢完全唔跟個食譜，隨心所欲咁去落<br />\n<br />\n我都覺得奇怪，於是就開聲問佢：「得個幾嚿牛油夠唔夠架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用奶粉得唔得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n之後佢就係到hea鳩我，乜都話得，又話是但無乜所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我就算冇整開，都知甜品呢啲野要跟足食譜，落岩分量，但佢講到咁，我咪由鳩佢囉<br />\n<br />\n咁焗完出黎，我見到個樣已經覺得伏伏地<br />\n<br />\n點知佢仲未玩完，仲要整cream<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n於是佢就又開始鳩整，唉屌又係屎<br />\n<br />\n到最後佢撚完一輪，叫我試食<br />\n<br />\n我咬左啖，哇屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未食過咁撚難食既蛋糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢自己食左啖，之後完全頂唔順掉撚曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我見佢咁on9，咪開口話佢兩句，叫佢下次做好準備，跟足份量步驟<br />\n<br />\n點知佢啲態度閪撚到呢，明明自己係有錯仲死唔認錯，係到死頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌，有著個咁撚on9既妹，我前世都唔知係做左啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7384c8bc8bfb28507b2c7b50a3b8bb92db020fd","tid":184074,"uid":36029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:29:01.000Z","msg":"先達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa4b121022a155dfebbe25ab3de53ce5f77c1862","tid":184074,"uid":11143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:30:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"767e3c2e34088eae8df3ffce84ff52cfd28d7ddb","tid":184074,"uid":14653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:30:47.000Z","msg":"屌你個妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9a10b126cbae82bece317edf34b90575c81307c","tid":184074,"uid":17759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:31:57.000Z","msg":"兜巴聲落去啦 仲等咩"},{"pid":"a6fc647a670a1d438b0b0d74c56b0cd607790b08","tid":184074,"uid":29719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:32:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>先達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"450389fc35a97ce0cf47d8206c34110c5443c565","tid":184074,"uid":92727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:32:46.000Z","msg":"妹妹緊係要屌，大大力"},{"pid":"d32dde4836db7bb167f3a52e5f16c4d60c43f7e2","tid":184074,"uid":29719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:32:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中出佢</blockquote><br />\n你屌埋我個份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d1f33ab3793ca1d54ee7a65b9eaced1df908171","tid":184074,"uid":29719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:34:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兜巴聲落去啦 仲等咩</blockquote><br />\n毒撚冇跟wu cfu健身唔敢郁手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢好撚高大 驚比佢打死"},{"pid":"139f6a9751df8b6962879080cdb5fa16918a9709","tid":184074,"uid":17759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:35:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>兜巴聲落去啦 